requires development.

93
00:07:50,445 --> 00:07:52,880
This is a healthy competition.

94
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:55,200
Competition over friendship.

95
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,700
You...

96
00:07:57,495 --> 00:07:59,350
You really don't know your limits.

97
00:07:59,350 --> 00:08:02,715
Just wait. I'll make you lose badly.

98
00:08:03,365 --> 00:08:06,470
Instead of crying out,
you'd better study harder.

99
00:08:06,470 --> 00:08:08,905
