 I'll bring you something, too. 

114
00:09:05,830 --> 00:09:08,480
Actions speak louder.

115
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:11,130
- Shu Lan.
- Don't get me wrong.

116
00:09:11,130 --> 00:09:13,510
