Brother Rui.

125
00:09:50,725 --> 00:09:53,060
 Wait. He's a first-year PhD. 

126
00:09:53,060 --> 00:09:55,820
 He can't sign up for my category. 

127
00:09:55,825 --> 00:09:58,555
 Am I really doing it alone? 

128
