Hi.

129
00:10:11,230 --> 00:10:13,520
Is that too casual?

130
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:15,750
Forget it.

131
00:10:18,775 --> 00:10:22,305
Come on. What does she take me for?

132
00:10:22,305 --> 00:10:24,100
As long as you take part in the contest
on behalf of your school,

133
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:27,740
I'll make sure that you win first place.

134
00:10:27,740 --> 00:10:31,155
That's my dear aunt. Awesome.

135
00:10:38,775 --> 00:10:39,830
Have a minute?

136
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:41,480
Not interested. It's boring.

137
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,990
I want to be like my idol.

138
00:10:42,990 --> 00:10:46,870
I'll head to conquer the stars
and the vast universe.

139
