in our group chat.

168
00:12:09,735 --> 00:12:11,935
Why am I not in the group?

169
00:12:16,295 --> 00:12:18,110
Mark my words.

170
00:12:18,110 --> 00:12:20,920
Without me, you don't stand a chance.

171
00:12:22,326 --> 00:12:26,526
Why are you so sure
that we can win with you?

172
