Stop it.

189
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:42,080
Have you developed
professional habits as a chauffeur?

190
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,480
Totally.

191
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:45,080
Tell you what.

192
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:48,800
I'm always thinking about serving my passengers.

193
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,920
- Take these.
- So many bags.

194
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:52,320
Come on.

195
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,320
Think about it.

196
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:59,970
Since we're doing better and better,
is it time for me to take a break?

197
00:13:59,970 --> 00:14:01,280
