198
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:05,020
Haven't you heard?
People fall sick when they are idle.

199
00:14:05,020 --> 00:14:07,320
You have a point.

200
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:09,320
The employees make money for the boss.

201
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:11,920
The money is not yours
unless you spend it today.

202
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:14,400
Let's go. Let's keep shopping somewhere else.

203
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:16,985
These are not for me,
but for our daughter.

204
00:14:16,985 --> 00:14:18,585
Look.

205
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:22,320
The weather and season are about to change.
I rushed to buy her new clothes.

206
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:24,240
