so they're together all the time.

212
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,200
Affection grew?

213
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:42,510
I bumped into them downstairs the other day.

214
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,710
Right on the spot?

215
00:14:43,710 --> 00:14:45,345
