It locks automatically.

220
00:15:02,110 --> 00:15:04,735
- My shoe almost fell off.
- Fasten your seat belt.

221
00:15:06,485 --> 00:15:08,535
Come on. To our team.

222
00:15:08,535 --> 00:15:10,855
Cheers!

223
00:15:14,340 --> 00:15:16,880
 

224
