225
00:15:26,940 --> 00:15:27,680
Hello.

226
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:30,585
You're a team of five now? How's it going?

227
00:15:30,585 --> 00:15:32,355
How do you know?

228
00:15:33,205 --> 00:15:35,990
That's why Wen Bo came so coincidentally.

229
00:15:35,990 --> 00:15:38,280
