with his own eyes,

234
00:15:50,470 --> 00:15:52,510
how could he join you?

235
00:15:53,175 --> 00:15:54,830
What an old fox.

236
00:15:54,830 --> 00:15:56,830
I'm having hot pot.

237
00:15:56,830 --> 00:15:57,990
