247
00:16:24,605 --> 00:16:25,410
Lin.

248
00:16:25,410 --> 00:16:27,870
Lin, what a small world.

249
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:29,400
You are...

250
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:32,110
