254
00:16:41,110 --> 00:16:45,015
Xue Jiao is having hot pot with her friends.

255
00:16:45,015 --> 00:16:47,655
Why didn't she invite you?

256
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,820
She...

257
00:16:51,605 --> 00:16:53,280
 I guess it didn't work out. 

258
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:55,295
 Keep observing. 

259
00:16:55,295 --> 00:16:58,470
It's okay. Let's take the things to her dorm.

260
00:16:58,470 --> 00:17:00,400
You are so busy. We can't trouble you.

261
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:01,680
It's okay.

262
00:17:01,680 --> 00:17:03,425
- Give it to me.
- You're so busy.

263
00:17:03,425 --> 00:17:04,825
Okay.

264
00:17:06,575 --> 00:17:08,120
Lin.

265
00:17:08,120 --> 00:17:09,880
