and my members are so easily agitated.

419
00:26:17,225 --> 00:26:20,495
It's impossible to lead them.

420
00:26:20,495 --> 00:26:23,160
It's because I've never been a leader.

421
00:26:23,940 --> 00:26:26,000
Come on, leader.

