459
00:29:10,240 --> 00:29:12,055
I stay up late every day.

460
00:29:12,055 --> 00:29:14,505
And my teammates are useless.

461
00:29:17,615 --> 00:29:18,790
Xue Jiao.

462
00:29:18,790 --> 00:29:20,457
